WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:47.160
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:51.480 --> 01:52.600
It's beautiful!

01:52.680 --> 01:53.760
So nice!

01:54.480 --> 01:56.400
‎BOUNTIFUL HARVEST FROM FIELDS AND LOOM

01:57.160 --> 01:58.400
Hurry!

01:59.080 --> 02:00.120
Be careful!

02:02.400 --> 02:03.320
So nice!

02:03.880 --> 02:05.680
-Nice, right?
-Very nice.

02:17.040 --> 02:17.880
My wife.

02:22.880 --> 02:25.960
Thank you for accompanying me
for another year.

02:28.880 --> 02:30.400
You old rascal.

02:30.480 --> 02:31.800
You still have such thoughts?

02:32.880 --> 02:35.440
The older you get,
the more thoughtful you should be.

02:37.200 --> 02:38.960
Otherwise, why would I pick you
as my partner?

02:39.040 --> 02:40.240
Ning wants one too.

02:42.240 --> 02:43.800
-You want one too?
-Ning wants one too!

02:43.880 --> 02:46.160
Your hands are too small.
It won't stay on.

02:46.240 --> 02:48.040
Ning wants a partner too.

02:49.800 --> 02:50.720
You want a partner?

02:55.400 --> 02:56.480
Look, over there.

03:12.520 --> 03:13.440
So…

03:15.000 --> 03:16.240
this is how New Year is celebrated.

03:17.920 --> 03:20.120
Happy New Year!

03:26.280 --> 03:28.280
Happy New Year!

03:38.200 --> 03:39.080
What did you say?

03:40.080 --> 03:41.240
Happy…

03:43.240 --> 03:44.440
New Year!

03:48.480 --> 03:49.840
Happy New Year.

03:52.360 --> 03:56.520
If you want the cub,
you must first feed the wolf.

04:03.520 --> 04:04.600
What cub?

04:25.800 --> 04:29.160
Are you really drunk or just pretending?

04:32.040 --> 04:33.600
Of course, I am pretending.

04:36.400 --> 04:37.600
You are truly drunk.

04:38.120 --> 04:39.920
Come, I'll take you back to the room.

04:40.000 --> 04:41.680
Don't move.

04:42.280 --> 04:43.480
Don't move.

04:54.520 --> 04:56.000
You must first feed the wolf…

04:59.920 --> 05:01.520
if you want the cub.

05:50.800 --> 05:53.200
Zheng, Changyu!

05:58.400 --> 06:01.240
-What's wrong?
-The fireworks are too loud. Can't sleep.

06:24.840 --> 06:26.240
Ning, take off her shoes.

06:27.480 --> 06:28.520
Okay.

06:43.880 --> 06:46.120
I'm helping Changyu
take off her padded jacket.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.480
No need.

06:52.200 --> 06:54.880
Taking off your sister's padded jacket now
will make her catch a cold.

06:56.280 --> 06:57.240
It's fine.

06:57.840 --> 06:59.280
Let your sister sleep like this.

06:59.880 --> 07:00.920
Go get the quilt.

07:24.960 --> 07:26.160
Changning.

07:29.400 --> 07:31.280
What happened in the room tonight…

07:31.800 --> 07:33.000
Don't tell your sister.

07:33.080 --> 07:34.480
What?

07:38.120 --> 07:39.160
Nothing.

08:10.680 --> 08:11.280
CERTAINLY RICH

08:11.360 --> 08:12.680
Zheng'er!

08:14.080 --> 08:15.040
Zheng'er!

08:22.600 --> 08:23.720
-Zheng'er!
-Mother!

08:25.960 --> 08:27.560
Being first day of the New Year,

08:27.640 --> 08:28.640
Zheng'er is so good.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.880
Actually didn't laze in bed.

08:30.840 --> 08:32.440
Search carefully around this room.

08:32.520 --> 08:35.360
I have prepared
a New Year's surprise for you.

08:40.200 --> 08:41.559
Thank you, Mother.

08:45.200 --> 08:46.840
Happy?

08:46.920 --> 08:48.000
Yes.

08:48.080 --> 08:50.520
Then Mother will tell you more good news.

08:51.240 --> 08:54.160
Father and Uncle will be returning
from the frontier soon.

09:37.040 --> 09:39.840
FORTUNE

09:39.920 --> 09:42.480
ICE MELTS, THE SPRINGS PULSE
SNOW CLEARS, YOUNG GRASS RISES

10:01.480 --> 10:03.080
What happened?

10:03.600 --> 10:05.560
Last night…

10:28.720 --> 10:30.360
-Morning.
-Morning.

10:43.960 --> 10:44.880
Happy New Year.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.040
Happy New Year.

10:51.680 --> 10:52.680
Something wrong?

10:54.760 --> 10:56.160
I just want to ask…

10:57.800 --> 11:00.000
Last night, you…

11:04.200 --> 11:05.760
Last night…

11:08.480 --> 11:10.440
Do you remember…

11:10.520 --> 11:11.440
I just want to say…

11:11.520 --> 11:13.240
Changyu! Changyu!

11:13.320 --> 11:15.200
I come to give you New Year's greetings!

11:16.840 --> 11:18.600
-Ms. Yu!
-Uncle, Auntie!

11:18.680 --> 11:21.720
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

11:21.800 --> 11:22.640
Happy New Year!

11:22.720 --> 11:23.920
What you wanted to tell me

11:24.000 --> 11:25.440
-was that they would come for greetings?
-Happy New Year!

11:26.680 --> 11:27.720
Happy New Year!

11:34.080 --> 11:36.080
Changyu, look who's here!

11:36.600 --> 11:37.640
Qian!

11:39.320 --> 11:41.520
Didn't expect it to be
so festive here at your place.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.680
So lively.

11:42.760 --> 11:43.600
Of course.

11:43.680 --> 11:46.400
Auntie Changyu, Uncle Yanzheng,
Happy New Year.

11:46.480 --> 11:48.920
Happy New Year. Your hat is really pretty.

11:50.160 --> 11:52.120
Alright, don't just stand talking.
Come inside quickly.

11:52.200 --> 11:54.440
Yes, please come inside.

11:54.960 --> 11:55.840
Come.

11:56.600 --> 11:57.640
This way.

12:04.360 --> 12:07.040
-What are these?
-Your coming already makes us very happy.

12:07.120 --> 12:08.560
Why bring such expensive things?

12:09.240 --> 12:11.320
You and your husband helped me so much.

12:11.400 --> 12:13.360
I don't even know how to thank you.

12:15.680 --> 12:18.360
That Qi grain merchant
didn't show up again later, right?

12:18.960 --> 12:19.920
With brother-in-law stepping in,

12:20.000 --> 12:20.920
everything is fine now.

12:23.640 --> 12:26.040
I looked forward to your coming every day,

12:26.120 --> 12:27.440
but you never came.

12:28.440 --> 12:29.880
We were busy those days.

12:29.960 --> 12:31.640
I had to help Changyu
prepare for the New Year.

12:32.320 --> 12:33.720
How does your family
celebrate the New Year?

12:33.800 --> 12:36.280
Just watch fireworks,

12:36.360 --> 12:37.640
eat spicy hot pot,

12:38.680 --> 12:40.160
write Spring Festival couplets,

12:40.240 --> 12:42.000
make snowmen, and play sledding.

12:43.280 --> 12:44.560
Did you eat candy?

12:47.400 --> 12:50.080
I secretly saved two pieces. One for you.

12:50.160 --> 12:51.240
Didn't dare take more.

12:51.320 --> 12:52.440
I am afraid you'll get cavities.

12:52.520 --> 12:53.800
Thank you, Changning.

12:56.080 --> 12:57.280
Eat slowly.

12:57.880 --> 12:58.960
Ms. Yu.

12:59.040 --> 13:00.720
Stay for a simple meal today.

13:00.800 --> 13:02.320
Big lamb dumplings.

13:03.040 --> 13:05.520
Although they are not as refined
as Yixiang Restaurant's food,

13:05.600 --> 13:07.640
-but it stands for family reunion.
-Yes, yes!

13:07.720 --> 13:09.080
Thank you, Auntie.

13:09.160 --> 13:11.560
I haven't had lamb dumplings
for a long time. Allow me to help too.

13:11.640 --> 13:12.760
No, no.

13:12.840 --> 13:14.600
Today, neither of you
will be allowed in the kitchen.

13:14.680 --> 13:15.840
Yes.

13:16.360 --> 13:17.840
What? You come help.

13:19.000 --> 13:20.080
Hurry up.

13:20.160 --> 13:21.080
Come on.

13:22.720 --> 13:23.960
Look at this.

13:25.280 --> 13:27.640
-You can handle this alone.
-I need your help.

13:27.720 --> 13:29.280
Want to have a snowball fight?

13:30.360 --> 13:31.760
But I have to ask my mother.

13:31.840 --> 13:32.960
I heard it.

13:34.120 --> 13:36.440
Fuling, take them to play.
Don't run too far.

13:36.520 --> 13:37.440
Okay.

13:39.200 --> 13:40.040
-Let's go.
-Go.

13:44.040 --> 13:46.440
Bao'er, look, my snowman has hands!

13:49.360 --> 13:50.960
How dare you hit me!

13:52.480 --> 13:54.440
Take my super snowball!

13:57.520 --> 13:58.560
Yu Bao'er!

14:02.280 --> 14:05.000
-You dare hit me? Look at my snowball!
-Take it.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.760
Such cute little kids.

14:14.520 --> 14:18.360
Here, take it. Happy New Year.

14:20.120 --> 14:21.240
Take it.

14:21.760 --> 14:23.360
I am getting old.

14:24.000 --> 14:26.920
I just wanted to borrow your hands
to seek some good fortune.

14:27.000 --> 14:28.160
Here.

14:28.680 --> 14:30.480
-Thank you.
-You are welcome.

14:30.560 --> 14:32.440
Thank you. Happy New Year, Granny.

14:33.280 --> 14:34.560
Happy New Year.

14:35.160 --> 14:36.760
What's your name?

14:36.840 --> 14:38.040
How old are you?

14:40.560 --> 14:41.840
My name is Cong'er.

14:41.920 --> 14:43.160
I am seven.

14:44.360 --> 14:46.800
About the same as my grandson.

14:46.880 --> 14:48.520
He was born in August.

14:48.600 --> 14:50.120
What month were you born in?

14:50.200 --> 14:51.400
The fifth day of May.

14:54.040 --> 14:55.840
Dragon Boat Festival.

14:55.920 --> 14:58.280
Auspicious day.

15:03.400 --> 15:04.240
Come!

15:04.320 --> 15:05.160
Changning!

15:08.440 --> 15:09.360
Changning!

15:09.440 --> 15:10.360
Bao'er!

15:11.680 --> 15:12.560
Come find me!

15:12.640 --> 15:13.480
Bao'er!

15:15.360 --> 15:16.280
Changning!

15:20.480 --> 15:21.480
Changning!

15:22.560 --> 15:23.440
Bao'er!

15:23.960 --> 15:25.080
Bao'er!

15:27.560 --> 15:28.400
Bao'er!

15:29.600 --> 15:30.720
-Yu Bao'er!
-Ning!

15:31.760 --> 15:32.960
Yu Bao'er!

15:33.040 --> 15:34.200
-Ning!
-My fault!

15:34.280 --> 15:36.040
We were making snowmen
at the village entrance,

15:36.120 --> 15:37.320
but I got distracted.

15:37.400 --> 15:39.400
In the blink of an eye,
I lost Ning and Bao'er.

15:39.480 --> 15:40.520
Bao'er!

15:40.600 --> 15:41.880
Don't worry. We'll definitely find them.

15:42.800 --> 15:43.960
Yu Bao'er!

15:44.040 --> 15:45.480
-Ning!
-Yu Bao'er!

15:58.440 --> 15:59.880
Finally hit you!

16:00.400 --> 16:01.480
Where did you go?

16:01.560 --> 16:03.440
Ning and I went for a snowball fight.

16:03.520 --> 16:04.480
The snow is thick over here.

16:05.240 --> 16:06.440
Why didn't you answer when we called?

16:06.520 --> 16:08.040
We couldn't find you anywhere
along the way.

16:08.120 --> 16:09.560
You scared me to death, do you know?!

16:10.200 --> 16:11.680
It's okay. We found them, didn't we?

16:11.760 --> 16:13.040
Kids love playing.

16:14.240 --> 16:15.280
It's alright now.

16:20.080 --> 16:20.920
You hit me!

16:25.760 --> 16:28.080
-Take it!
-Yu Bao'er!

16:28.840 --> 16:30.000
You are done.

16:30.080 --> 16:31.000
Yu Bao'er!

17:05.040 --> 17:06.560
Give me that!

17:26.480 --> 17:27.359
My lord,

17:27.960 --> 17:30.880
that child somewhat looks like you
when you were young,

17:30.960 --> 17:32.800
but the birth date doesn't match.

17:34.040 --> 17:35.160
Is that so?

17:53.520 --> 17:54.360
Speak.

17:54.960 --> 17:56.120
When is your

17:56.760 --> 17:58.200
young master's birthday?

17:59.840 --> 18:02.720
It’s… the year of Dingchou,

18:02.800 --> 18:03.720
the ninth day of August.

18:04.320 --> 18:05.520
Named Bao'er.

18:08.120 --> 18:09.120
Hear that?

18:10.000 --> 18:11.640
Just like his mother,

18:12.160 --> 18:13.760
he loves to lie.

18:13.840 --> 18:16.160
Don't kill me!

18:21.320 --> 18:23.560
This amout of money
is enough for the rest of your life.

18:24.280 --> 18:25.720
Leave Lin'an. Don't come back.

18:26.560 --> 18:27.400
Thank you, sir.

18:28.000 --> 18:29.120
Thank you.

18:30.720 --> 18:33.240
I will bring the young master home
right away.

18:39.440 --> 18:41.720
Nanny Lan is getting
more and more assertive.

18:55.760 --> 18:57.880
I know my crime. Know my crime!

19:06.880 --> 19:08.560
You have taken care of me for many years,

19:09.840 --> 19:11.360
wholeheartedly worried for me.

19:13.280 --> 19:14.360
What crime is there?

19:17.240 --> 19:18.320
Don't worry.

19:19.200 --> 19:21.920
My child will be found sooner or later.

19:22.560 --> 19:25.120
It's just that we still have dealings
with Marquis Wu'an now.

19:25.840 --> 19:27.600
I don't want to shake that relationship.

19:29.840 --> 19:30.840
Don't worry.

19:31.480 --> 19:33.560
They can't escape from Lin'an Town.

19:35.000 --> 19:36.400
You are wise, my lord.

19:36.920 --> 19:38.840
I was too impatient.

19:58.160 --> 19:59.920
Come and have a look!

20:00.000 --> 20:01.960
Sir, here you go.

20:02.040 --> 20:03.960
Take a look here!

20:04.040 --> 20:06.240
Rob in the day…

20:11.040 --> 20:12.320
Military Commissioner Wei
ordered to requisition grain.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.520
-You dare resist?!
-Stop it!

20:15.120 --> 20:16.280
Please forgive me!

20:17.840 --> 20:19.360
This is Jizhou.

20:19.440 --> 20:20.760
Governor He has the order.

20:21.360 --> 20:23.160
Soliders are forbidden from contending
with the people for grain.

20:24.080 --> 20:25.440
Seize them!

20:25.520 --> 20:26.720
Who dares?!

20:33.720 --> 20:34.800
Take them away!

20:37.520 --> 20:38.520
-Move!
-Hurry!

20:38.600 --> 20:39.800
We are Lord Wei's soldiers!

20:39.880 --> 20:41.400
You dare arrest us?

20:42.600 --> 20:43.440
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

20:43.520 --> 20:46.040
Should we attack their left
or their right?

20:46.760 --> 20:49.240
Divide our forces into three routes
to surround them.

20:49.320 --> 20:50.160
-Cut off their grain supply…
-He Jingyuan!

20:51.040 --> 20:52.360
Get out here!

20:56.120 --> 20:57.400
Young Master.

20:57.480 --> 20:59.920
What's the matter, so frantic?

21:00.000 --> 21:02.080
How dare you!

21:02.640 --> 21:04.480
You dared to arrest my men!

21:04.560 --> 21:06.240
Please calm down.

21:08.600 --> 21:09.760
Young Master.

21:10.600 --> 21:12.280
Those soldiers were on the streets

21:12.360 --> 21:14.560
forcibly requisitioning
the common people's grain.

21:14.640 --> 21:15.840
It aroused public anger.

21:15.920 --> 21:18.040
So we had to temporarily detain them.

21:19.520 --> 21:21.880
The recent events
are indeed a bit strange.

21:21.960 --> 21:22.920
I'm thinking,

21:23.000 --> 21:26.200
it must be interlocked stratagems

21:26.280 --> 21:28.040
set by those Prince Changxin rebels.

21:29.040 --> 21:32.160
Therefore, I advise the Young Master,

21:32.240 --> 21:35.120
you must not fall into their trap!

21:35.200 --> 21:36.160
Interlocked stratagems?

21:36.920 --> 21:38.520
We've only lost a few battles.

21:38.600 --> 21:40.880
Then you're convinced
I can't take Chongzhou?

21:42.440 --> 21:44.520
Arrest my men, hold my grain,

21:44.600 --> 21:46.560
and look down upon me!

21:46.640 --> 21:48.280
-Young Master--
-Deliberately shaking military morale

21:48.360 --> 21:49.600
is aiding the enemy!

21:49.680 --> 21:51.280
-Guards!
-Here!

21:51.360 --> 21:54.440
Take He Jingyuan
and throw him in prison, pending trial.

21:54.520 --> 21:55.920
-Who dares?!
-Wait!

21:57.880 --> 21:58.840
What are you doing?

21:58.920 --> 22:00.240
Do you want to start an internal conflict?

22:01.280 --> 22:03.640
Wouldn't that be
the rebels' treacherous plot?

22:09.880 --> 22:10.960
Young master.

22:12.280 --> 22:15.120
I advise you one last time.

22:15.800 --> 22:17.120
Please be prudent.

22:27.800 --> 22:29.520
-Take him away!
-Yes!

22:34.600 --> 22:36.240
-General!
-General!

22:36.760 --> 22:38.000
-General!
-General!

22:39.320 --> 22:40.480
TOKEN

22:46.240 --> 22:48.480
Follow my order
as the Northwest Military Commissioner.

22:49.120 --> 22:51.440
Immediately requisition grain in Jizhou.

22:52.040 --> 22:53.720
In three days, at noon,

22:53.800 --> 22:56.560
if I don't see 100,000 dan of grain,

22:57.400 --> 22:59.080
then bring me your heads.

23:04.440 --> 23:06.560
One hundred thousand dan of grain…

23:07.080 --> 23:08.680
That’s impossible.

23:08.760 --> 23:09.960
General He was taken away.

23:10.040 --> 23:11.520
Our lives were also being threatened.

23:12.200 --> 23:14.240
Commandant Li happens to be absent.

23:14.320 --> 23:15.800
What are we to do?

23:17.920 --> 23:20.480
LANTERN FESTIVAL

23:24.680 --> 23:26.080
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

23:28.560 --> 23:29.680
-Good!
-Bravo!

23:29.760 --> 23:31.040
Good.

23:32.480 --> 23:35.200
Haven't been to the Lantern Festival
for long. So lively.

23:35.280 --> 23:36.800
XIANGSHENG TROUPE

23:41.120 --> 23:43.080
-Look at that!
-Come and have a look!

23:45.520 --> 23:47.880
-Lanterns!
-Look, this one moves! Look!

23:47.960 --> 23:49.240
Come take a look!

23:49.840 --> 23:52.400
-Let's go.
-We won't return to Xigu Alley tonight.

23:52.480 --> 23:53.480
Why?

23:54.480 --> 23:57.480
A banquet tomorrow at Yixiang Restaurant
needs lots of stewed pork.

23:58.120 --> 24:00.400
Qian wants me to go help tomorrow.

24:02.800 --> 24:04.040
Come, let me hold you up.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.240
Careful!

24:24.200 --> 24:25.520
That's beautiful!

24:28.200 --> 24:30.040
Then let's find an inn.

24:30.840 --> 24:32.280
Qian has already arranged it.

24:32.360 --> 24:33.480
We can stay at her place.

24:37.600 --> 24:38.720
Fireworks!

24:39.680 --> 24:40.720
‎I like it.

24:40.800 --> 24:41.800
Maybe I should carry her.

24:42.720 --> 24:44.680
The injury on your hand isn't healed yet.

24:44.760 --> 24:46.160
It's fine to carry a child.

24:46.240 --> 24:47.280
I see on this street,

24:47.360 --> 24:50.240
all the children are being carried
by fathers or brothers.

24:55.240 --> 24:56.760
Let me know when you feel tired.

24:56.840 --> 24:57.960
Sure.

24:58.040 --> 24:59.800
-Which way?
-That way.

25:00.560 --> 25:01.760
Over there!

25:12.080 --> 25:13.120
Look at that!

25:54.640 --> 25:56.160
Take a look!

25:56.240 --> 25:58.600
Making wishes on a festive lantern
is most effective!

25:58.680 --> 26:00.800
Miss it, you'll have to wait another year!

26:00.880 --> 26:03.160
Dear sir and madam, want to buy one?

26:17.200 --> 26:18.280
Do you want one?

26:18.360 --> 26:19.600
That's alright.

26:19.680 --> 26:20.520
Let‘s go.

26:42.520 --> 26:43.440
What's wrong?

26:53.680 --> 26:57.040
Look, they all have Song Yan's name
written on them.

26:57.120 --> 26:58.600
What kind of "good man" is he?

26:59.560 --> 27:02.040
When did these young girls go blind?

27:02.640 --> 27:04.800
Making wishes for marrying him
is just digging their own graves.

27:06.120 --> 27:07.040
No.

27:07.760 --> 27:09.160
What are you going to do?

27:09.240 --> 27:10.280
Save them.

27:10.360 --> 27:12.000
TO SONG YAN

27:13.960 --> 27:15.280
No, if you erase it like this,

27:15.360 --> 27:16.480
you'll get beaten if they see this.

27:16.560 --> 27:18.440
I'm saving them.

27:18.960 --> 27:20.520
There's a saying,

27:23.400 --> 27:24.600
"Although the cart in front overturned,

27:25.400 --> 27:27.360
we won't let the cart behind
also fall into the pit."

27:32.840 --> 27:34.480
There are so many lanterns in this river.

27:34.560 --> 27:36.000
How long will it take you
to erase them all?

27:37.800 --> 27:39.880
Are they losing their minds?

27:46.120 --> 27:49.240
It seems you also set a lantern
for Song Yan before, right?

27:50.440 --> 27:53.520
The money I saved
all went for his tuition.

27:53.600 --> 27:55.200
How could I buy it?

27:56.640 --> 27:59.440
Ning wants that piggy lantern
over there too.

28:00.400 --> 28:01.480
Go.

28:03.640 --> 28:04.480
Be careful.

28:07.480 --> 28:08.480
Let's go.

28:16.080 --> 28:17.720
Song Yan…

28:21.560 --> 28:24.400
TEAHOUSE

28:45.080 --> 28:46.040
Pick one.

28:46.560 --> 28:47.480
I want this one.

28:52.280 --> 28:53.960
Changyu.

28:54.040 --> 28:55.080
Changyu.

29:05.600 --> 29:06.680
Changyu.

29:06.760 --> 29:08.000
Good dogs know to stay out of the way.

29:08.080 --> 29:08.920
Changyu.

29:09.520 --> 29:10.760
Sorry.

29:12.600 --> 29:14.440
Have you always regretted
never setting a lantern?

29:15.280 --> 29:16.640
I'll make it up to you.

29:16.720 --> 29:18.200
Write both our names on it. How about it?

29:18.280 --> 29:19.440
Disgusting!

29:20.520 --> 29:22.240
Everything I say is sincere.

29:23.120 --> 29:24.360
Sincere?

29:30.840 --> 29:32.320
Everyone, come look!

29:32.920 --> 29:35.800
This provincial graduate
gives me a lantern!

29:35.880 --> 29:37.880
-He says he's sincerely apologizing to me!
-Stop it!

29:37.960 --> 29:39.200
And he wants to give a latern!

29:39.280 --> 29:40.120
-Everyone, quick--
-Shut up!

29:41.320 --> 29:42.160
What?

29:42.760 --> 29:44.680
You dare say it,
but not let everyone hear?

29:46.000 --> 29:47.440
It's clearly you who can't forget me.

29:48.040 --> 29:50.120
I'm just humoring your infatuation
because of old times.

29:50.200 --> 29:52.240
-You…
-Brother Yan.

29:58.600 --> 30:01.120
Fan Changyu.

30:01.800 --> 30:02.880
My love!

30:03.520 --> 30:04.560
My love!

30:06.120 --> 30:08.040
I came to buy you a lantern,

30:08.120 --> 30:11.560
but saw Changyu,
still unable to forget me,

30:11.640 --> 30:13.000
being jealous.

30:13.080 --> 30:14.720
She scratched off others' lanterns.

30:14.800 --> 30:15.720
That's why I stepped in to stop.

30:15.800 --> 30:16.800
Bullshit!

30:18.040 --> 30:21.400
I wanted to pull
these young girls out of trouble.

30:21.480 --> 30:22.600
Fan Changyu!

30:23.120 --> 30:25.400
You really are

30:26.080 --> 30:27.760
deeply in love with our Brother Yan.

30:29.480 --> 30:32.000
You knew he would come
to the lantern festival tonight,

30:32.080 --> 30:33.680
so you eagerly came,

30:33.760 --> 30:35.080
just to see him.

30:36.640 --> 30:38.200
It's her who has always
been unable to forget me.

30:38.280 --> 30:40.280
And she's still here,
scratching off others' lanterns.

30:40.360 --> 30:41.320
Song Yan…

30:42.960 --> 30:45.040
Clearly already a married woman,

30:45.120 --> 30:47.440
yet day after day
comes to harass Brother Yan.

30:47.520 --> 30:49.520
Really clingy and persistent.

30:49.600 --> 30:52.560
I've never seen someone so shameless.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.320
Our relationship has ended.

30:55.400 --> 30:56.560
Stop pestering me.

30:57.440 --> 30:58.400
My love!

30:58.920 --> 30:59.760
Let's go over there.

30:59.840 --> 31:01.080
-No.
-Miss Cui!

31:01.680 --> 31:03.320
This trash, Song Yan,

31:03.400 --> 31:04.320
I don't mind giving him to you.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.920
But I'd like to offer you advice.

31:06.000 --> 31:07.480
He

31:08.120 --> 31:10.320
enjoys two-timing.

31:10.400 --> 31:12.000
Don't let him fool you.

31:13.440 --> 31:14.600
What are you saying?

31:15.800 --> 31:19.160
A pig-slaughtering woman couldn't become
a provincial graduate‘s wife,

31:19.840 --> 31:21.640
so you dare slander him here?

31:26.120 --> 31:27.520
This fellow Song

31:27.600 --> 31:29.800
will definitely seek out
higher-ranking nobles in the future,

31:29.880 --> 31:31.320
climb to a taller branch.

31:32.000 --> 31:33.160
You and the Magistrate

31:33.240 --> 31:35.280
are just stepping stones
for him and his mother.

31:36.480 --> 31:39.360
Otherwise, why has he delayed
proposing to your family for so long?

31:43.000 --> 31:44.480
Nonsense!

31:47.800 --> 31:48.920
My love!

31:49.600 --> 31:51.360
My feelings for you are sincere.

31:55.720 --> 31:56.800
Fan Changyu!

31:56.880 --> 31:57.920
I know

31:58.520 --> 31:59.960
you want to use these words

32:00.720 --> 32:02.560
to drive a wedge
between me and my Brother Yan.

32:03.160 --> 32:06.000
Our Brother Yan
just prioritizes his studies, that's all.

32:06.080 --> 32:07.720
Prioritizes his studies?

32:08.720 --> 32:12.080
When you made that promise
to me ten years ago,

32:12.160 --> 32:13.760
"prioritizing studies" was your excuse.

32:13.840 --> 32:15.600
Now ten years passed,
still stick to that, huh?

32:16.200 --> 32:17.520
-Stop talking nonsense!
-You!

32:18.600 --> 32:19.480
Fine.

32:20.760 --> 32:21.960
Then we'll see.

32:24.880 --> 32:25.760
-My love!
-Stop!

32:33.160 --> 32:35.360
Song, apologize.

32:35.440 --> 32:37.160
Why should I apologize to her?

32:37.240 --> 32:39.520
Flirted with a married woman
on the street,

32:40.120 --> 32:42.520
failed, then slandered her.

32:43.680 --> 32:45.200
Is this the behavior of a scholar?

32:46.000 --> 32:47.800
Forgot the rites of a gentleman?

32:48.320 --> 32:50.040
But you are quite skilled at gossiping.

32:51.280 --> 32:52.160
What?

32:53.160 --> 32:54.280
Came out of Fengxiao Pavilion?

32:55.480 --> 32:57.560
What did you say? You…

32:59.600 --> 33:01.080
What are you laughing at?

33:01.160 --> 33:02.040
You…

33:02.600 --> 33:03.760
You disgraced refinement!

33:03.840 --> 33:06.120
Refinement? Are you worthy of this word?

33:06.200 --> 33:07.480
Studied for just a few days,

33:07.560 --> 33:09.240
now you have eyes above the sky.

33:09.840 --> 33:10.840
How would you know?

33:11.560 --> 33:13.040
The northern geese fly south

33:13.560 --> 33:15.600
to the place of phoenixes
and the geese find it hard to land.

33:17.400 --> 33:20.280
It's clearly Changyu who couldn't
forget me, Song Yan, first.

33:21.760 --> 33:22.720
Song Yan?

33:24.600 --> 33:27.000
-Who is that?
-It is…

33:27.080 --> 33:30.320
My sister forgot about you,
this big bad guy, long ago!

33:32.400 --> 33:33.440
This kid…

33:37.080 --> 33:39.800
-Here, he left. Why?
-He just left!

33:42.320 --> 33:43.360
Not happy?

33:45.200 --> 33:48.120
Somehow, I still feel unsatisfied.

33:51.520 --> 33:52.640
Coming out for the lantern market

33:52.720 --> 33:54.000
and running into Fan Changyu.

33:54.080 --> 33:55.280
Unlucky.

33:56.720 --> 33:59.280
My love! No need to be bothered
by such a vulgar person.

34:00.440 --> 34:01.400
Take care of yourself.

34:01.960 --> 34:03.120
Then I'll head back first.

34:03.200 --> 34:04.280
My love!

34:07.200 --> 34:09.320
Take care.

34:20.520 --> 34:22.320
A pretty live-in son-in-law.

34:22.400 --> 34:24.760
If he really had the ability
to take the imperial exams,

34:24.840 --> 34:27.400
he wouldn't have to be
someone's live-in son-in-law.

34:29.600 --> 34:31.120
In my opinion,

34:31.199 --> 34:32.800
if he really took the imperial exams,

34:33.560 --> 34:36.120
he probably wouldn't even
pass the first-level exam.

34:38.320 --> 34:39.320
One.

34:40.000 --> 34:41.120
Two.

34:42.080 --> 34:43.159
Three.

34:44.960 --> 34:45.920
Four.

34:46.520 --> 34:47.800
Why are you hitting me?

34:47.880 --> 34:48.920
Five.

34:49.600 --> 34:50.600
Don't hit the face!

34:50.679 --> 34:51.560
Six.

34:51.639 --> 34:52.719
Be gentle!

34:53.760 --> 34:54.719
Seven.

34:56.159 --> 34:58.200
I only counted to seven!

35:06.640 --> 35:07.520
Wait.

35:08.040 --> 35:10.000
No need to run. He can't catch up.

35:14.760 --> 35:15.600
Ning.

35:41.360 --> 35:42.440
It's snowing.

35:56.200 --> 35:57.280
What's wrong?

35:59.040 --> 36:00.680
Your hair is messy.

36:01.480 --> 36:02.440
Turn around.

36:55.360 --> 36:56.680
Ning wants to do it too.

37:22.080 --> 37:22.960
Immortal Brother!

37:24.000 --> 37:25.200
Ning.

37:25.280 --> 37:28.040
Long time no see.
You‘re even more adorable.

37:30.720 --> 37:31.720
Mr. Sun.

37:32.360 --> 37:34.920
Mrs. Fan. Brother Yan.

37:35.960 --> 37:36.960
What brought you here?

37:37.040 --> 37:40.080
Just now, from the pavilion upstairs,
I saw you.

37:40.160 --> 37:41.000
So lovely.

37:41.080 --> 37:44.520
You two are truly a match.

37:45.120 --> 37:48.280
Even the little girl
is so charming, isn't she?

37:49.000 --> 37:50.440
So, I painted a picture.

37:51.120 --> 37:53.520
Consider it a New Year's gift for you.

37:53.600 --> 37:55.600
Wish your family harmony
in the coming year,

37:55.680 --> 37:57.760
and maybe with a little baby.

38:00.040 --> 38:01.560
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

38:02.280 --> 38:03.520
You came to Lin'an just to paint?

38:03.600 --> 38:05.960
No, I do have proper business.

38:06.040 --> 38:08.120
So, I need to borrow
your husband for a bit.

38:10.120 --> 38:11.720
You take Ning to play for a while first.

38:11.800 --> 38:13.440
I'll chat with Mr. Sun for a bit.

38:14.960 --> 38:17.000
-Take the umbrella.
-Let's go.

38:18.240 --> 38:19.080
Let's go.

38:24.960 --> 38:26.000
Wei Xuan has just been defeated.

38:26.080 --> 38:28.680
He Jingyuan was imprisoned
because of the grain requisition.

38:28.760 --> 38:30.480
Now the soldiers of Jizhou and Yanzhou

38:30.560 --> 38:32.960
all have quite a bit of resentment
towards the new Military Commissioner.

38:33.480 --> 38:34.680
Li Huaian is stuck in the capital.

38:34.760 --> 38:36.880
At the moment, the Jizhou army
is leaderless.

38:36.960 --> 38:38.200
The situation is exactly as you predicted.

38:38.800 --> 38:40.600
That old traitor Prince Changxin

38:40.680 --> 38:43.200
will definitely seize this opportunity
and prepare to act.

38:44.480 --> 38:46.200
The situation is becoming
increasingly critical.

38:46.280 --> 38:47.480
It's time for you to return.

38:51.880 --> 38:53.360
We've known each other so long,

38:53.440 --> 38:54.720
but I still don't know
when your birthday is.

38:55.640 --> 38:57.400
My birthday is easy to remember.

38:57.480 --> 38:58.920
Two days after the Lantern Festival.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.160
The New Year atmosphere
is still strong then.

39:00.240 --> 39:01.640
Lively and bustling.

39:08.640 --> 39:09.640
Three days from now,

39:10.320 --> 39:11.280
we set out.

39:13.160 --> 39:14.200
Aren’t you leaving toninght?

39:20.960 --> 39:22.080
-Let‘s move ahead.
-Okay.

39:22.160 --> 39:23.400
Anything else you want?

39:23.920 --> 39:24.800
Want a rattle-drum?

39:24.880 --> 39:25.880
Yes!

39:27.080 --> 39:28.480
Alright, understood.

39:30.520 --> 39:33.360
How's the investigation
into the Fan family going?

39:34.200 --> 39:35.600
So far, we only found out

39:35.680 --> 39:38.000
that Mrs. Fan's father
met He Jingyuan before he died.

39:39.560 --> 39:41.880
The two might be old acquaintances.

39:42.560 --> 39:44.960
But we didn't find any connection
between him and Wei Yan.

39:46.120 --> 39:47.200
This Sui Yuanhuai

39:47.280 --> 39:49.360
did find out that during the time
I was assassinated,

39:50.360 --> 39:52.480
Wei Yan secretly killed
family guards from back then.

39:53.080 --> 39:54.040
Who?

39:55.200 --> 39:57.000
Sui Yuanhuai, the eldest son
of Prince Changxin?

39:57.600 --> 39:59.160
You ran into him here?

39:59.240 --> 40:00.600
What did he come to Lin'an for?

40:00.680 --> 40:01.560
Because of you.

40:03.440 --> 40:04.680
Probably not for me.

40:06.680 --> 40:09.560
But if he came to Lin’an
for that lady, Ms. Yu,

40:10.200 --> 40:11.280
that doesn't make sense.

40:11.360 --> 40:12.960
And who is Ms. Yu?

40:13.600 --> 40:15.680
I left only half a month,

40:15.760 --> 40:17.440
and now I can't even understand you.

40:18.040 --> 40:19.560
Tell me in detail.

40:27.720 --> 40:28.680
I see.

40:29.320 --> 40:31.640
You've been quite diligent recently.

40:31.720 --> 40:32.800
What?

40:32.880 --> 40:34.880
Not trapped by that chess game?

40:38.280 --> 40:39.840
Some endgames

40:41.000 --> 40:42.760
can't be solved in a short while.

40:44.480 --> 40:45.480
I want to set them aside.

40:49.880 --> 40:51.360
How did you get Li Huaian away?

40:55.040 --> 40:56.680
What ability do I have?

40:56.760 --> 40:59.680
It was just a coincidence.

41:00.280 --> 41:04.680
CAPITAL

41:04.760 --> 41:06.360
SHENGXING STORE

41:23.040 --> 41:24.000
Commandant Li.

41:26.200 --> 41:29.200
You accompanied me today, drinking,
watching plays, listening to music.

41:30.320 --> 41:31.560
Are you tired of those?

41:32.280 --> 41:33.680
It is my honor.

41:36.280 --> 41:37.320
Honor?

41:38.680 --> 41:39.560
Frankly speaking,

41:40.080 --> 41:41.360
I have no feelings for you.

41:43.640 --> 41:44.960
Thank you for your frankness, Princess.

41:46.560 --> 41:49.040
But marriage is the elders' command.

41:49.960 --> 41:51.040
It's not what I seek either.

42:05.800 --> 42:06.840
You all may leave.

42:32.720 --> 42:33.920
I have a plan.

42:34.720 --> 42:36.000
Both of us will gain peace.

42:36.520 --> 42:37.360
How about it?

42:38.560 --> 42:39.400
I'd like to know it.

42:49.960 --> 42:52.600
I will go inform them
on behalf of Your Honor.

42:52.680 --> 42:55.680
No need. Don't disturb them.

43:07.960 --> 43:11.120
It's late. Rest early.

43:11.760 --> 43:13.240
Thank you, Fuling.

43:23.240 --> 43:26.840
This must be the surprise Qian mentioned.

46:05.840 --> 46:09.360
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:09.440 --> 46:10.280
Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
